{"tid":2189540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方擔心明午再有暴力場面 呼籲市民不要到旺角一帶","createTime":"2020-09-05T03:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T03:54:33.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"05752838367ba31022483775661ee7dfc9607801","tid":2189540,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:24:24.000Z","msg":"網上有人號召，明天下午於油尖旺區發起遊行。警方表示，這個活動並沒有獲得警方不反對通知書，預料明天風險頗高，警方會有足夠警力部署，以應對違法行為，呼籲市民不要到旺角一帶。消息指，警方擔心明天會有勇武派示威者出現，可能再有暴力場面，警方明天會步署超過2,000名警員應對。 警方昨日在社交網站表示，不容忍任何違法行為，再次呼籲市民不要參與任何未經批准集結或受禁的羣組聚集。警方會在相關地點部署足夠警力，迅速果斷執法，適時作出拘捕。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2355855&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs45mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=c8bc7056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2355855</a>"},{"pid":"1199c811119b7bbe5401a193500b481eb98943af","tid":2189540,"uid":264245,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"亂拉就亂拉喇，次次暴力場面都係黑警"},{"pid":"c9ea7ac67d129cc5cad4287c2a60663baa3edda7","tid":2189540,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"藍店要收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358a09eeab850cd1b1c38ea60b58f16de92ce012","tid":2189540,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:26:31.000Z","msg":"戒嚴未"},{"pid":"369baa0b26549e5b45d19b46d4e05726585e5dff","tid":2189540,"uid":56819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"冇黑警就唔會有暴力場面囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8a92fcad8e8aa44e395ec973e6f2d677689b84","tid":2189540,"uid":159271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"咁大家去銅鑼灣shopping."},{"pid":"cde0064637fc56104f49ff216d840e3afddbeb81","tid":2189540,"uid":50386,"lik